Tests For The Enigma Engine:

Validating the Enigma Engine:
    -   rotors, plug board are correctly initialised by the machineABC.
    -   reflectors are correctly initialised by the machineABC by length.
    -   selected rotors exist in rotors HashMap.
    -   all the components(rotors, reflectors, plug board nad machineABC) are in even size.
    -   size of startingCharacters is equal to the number of selected rotors.
    -   startingCharacters is a valid set of characters.